show.description: With the shocking revelation that her coma was fabricated, Isabella's quest for truth intensifies in this riveting second chapter. Armed with Detective Gonzalez's help and fragments of returning memories, she launches a dangerous counteroffensive against Stella, who has now fully embedded herself in the family's empire. As Antonio fights for his freedom from behind bars, Isabella must navigate a web of conspiracies that run deeper than she ever imagined—revealing powerful enemies who orchestrated her disappearance.
